Cell[TextData[{
 "Conditional heteroscedastic models are used for modeling ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   SubsuperscriptBox["\[Sigma]", "t", "2"], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "8b0110da-e6e3-4188-a16d-f953c59c4d7c"],
 " as an volatility estimate by \"allowing\" heteroscedasticity \
(time-variation) and capturing that dependence.\n\nDiscussion of the reading\n\
IGARCH\nForecasting with GARCH\nEWMA\nGARCH-t\nTAR-GARCH\nEGARCH\n\
Introduction to Long memory\nLong memory in volatility\n"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.3965463361661186`*^9, 3.39654633621592*^9}, {
